<item>
            <title>[PIG-292] Order by on more than one field returns wrong order</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-292</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Pig scripts with order by of a single column work fine.  But once a second column is added the data is returned in the wrong order.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
